Diagnostics Channels

Late Read Count

The Late Read Count channel is incremented any time the read loop in the engine returns late.

Timeout?

The Timeout? channel is asserted any time a read or write command times out. It is deasserted when a read or write is successfully executed without timing out.

Error

The Error group contains channels that report information on LabVIEW errors.
Click here for more information on the Error group.
